Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.80,0:02:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.83,0:02:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}悔恨的雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没有空联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果一直喝到早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有早饭吧 那我到下面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年一定要去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我一个人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎啊 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸫买的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么贵的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 又来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得有些不安吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 步美已经离开那么多年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那么年幼的小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 现在已经能那么拿手地做这栗子饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是你太太的忌日吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前妻而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事你怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天小鸫来学栗子饭的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是妈妈最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学生时代就认识了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有了孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是年轻的代价吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授会的报告是下一期的看点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.70,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采访被人拒绝就轻易放弃了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田那个家伙好像搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才发那么大火啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来对方怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫小川 到去年为止一起学语言学的文静女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底明不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小川步美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格和柴田完全相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是柴田对她一见钟情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把两年的感情都发泄在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有空说些闲事的话就快去校稿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概要陪他到早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.00,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众目睽睽之下你突然那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没有想到这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会在你面前出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果我可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 完全没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.30,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我们里面柴田那小子会第一个结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算是那么意外的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对步美小姐是一往情深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下前总理家里来了东京地检的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎会有大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能那就是不祥之兆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林纪子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七中央宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是脸色不太好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一会儿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女又告诉我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次地方和名字都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.90,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉阿一的话 他一定会去阻止地狱少女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.40,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可能他会理解地狱少女的所作所为是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也没有食欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫打来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么简单的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林纪子 第七中央宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地狱少女吗 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记我帐上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.90,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 纪子我已经住厌了现在的公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景也不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了 我帮你买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 真是个奢侈的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.10,0:11:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正圭一你很有钱嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七中央宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦快点 事态紧急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.90,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过安全驾驶更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽量快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 堵车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人你是做媒体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.90,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开出租车还没过半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过做媒体的人我还能看得出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早到晚 连回家看看的时间都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实就是那种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人你们家也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 马上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个的发电厂发生了事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有眉目了我打电话给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡着就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七点回来 会打电话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.60,0:14:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子出生的话 也许他会比现在稍微…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸫出生后阿一也没有变呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.10,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有了孩子比以前工作得更卖力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美是多么难过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.90,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七中央宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.60,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去蹲点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.20,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我和平时一样好几天没有回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在蹲点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.80,0:15:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以廉洁著称的政治家传言暗中有外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 柴田怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 前辈	
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 柴田 住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.60,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追查外遇的男人的老婆正是那个外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是个笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 发票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 长衫准备好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你做了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把一个人送进地狱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是对她来说我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所有男人只不过是摇钱树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种女人怎么能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能原谅的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她趁我上班的时候和男人搞外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈你也看到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还丢下鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你也替小鸫想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要母亲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要搞外遇的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最痛苦的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上大学时开始我就只喜欢她一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其品味这痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如当初没遇到她好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以索性要她消失好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使自己也会被送下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 这位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起的 突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成钱了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说男人就是钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位先生 请救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五日元也可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蠢的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想重归于好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛过的人还能相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不想让你见鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 别再让我见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有你最喜欢的钱的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你永远出不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都是那些男人们主动接近我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要受这份罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你不会有人想要接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.10,0:22:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨也只能换来空虚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.70,0:22:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以复仇是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.90,0:22:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要说委托别人去复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.90,0:22:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.80,0:22:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.40,0:23:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
