Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.80,0:24:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 真的是她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.20,0:24:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么受人爱戴和喜欢的那个姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.10,0:24:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被送进地狱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.10,0:24:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了别人努力工作的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.30,0:24:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.90,0:24:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.50,0:24:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 我开始混乱了
